OL,3,C'I felt abandoned': Man who lost job
OL,4,Cafter strokes settles case for #100,000
OL,6,FA man who lost his job after he had
OL,7,Ftwo strokes said he "lost sleep" and
OL,8,F"couldn't think about anything else"
OL,9,Fduring the ordeal.
OL,11,FClifford Donaldson has settled a
OL,12,Fdisability and age discrimination case
OL,13,Fagainst his former employer for
OL,14,F#100,000.
OL,16,FProperty developer Fraser Partners Ltd
OL,17,Fsettled the case with Mr Donaldson,
OL,18,Fwho was supported by the Equality
OL,19,FCommission for Northern Ireland,
OL,20,Fwithout admission of liability.
