OL,3,C'I felt abandoned': Man who lost job
OL,4,Cafter strokes settles case for #100,000
OL,6,FMr Donaldson was employed by the firm
OL,7,Fas a site manager for more than seven
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FIn January 2023, he had two strokes
OL,11,Fthat impacted his speech and movement.
OL,13,FAfter a short period of sick leave, he
OL,14,Freturned to work on a phased basis.
OL,16,FMr Donaldson said he asked for a
OL,17,Freduction in his working hours to 30
OL,18,Fhours a week, with a reduced salary.
