OL,3,C'I felt abandoned': Man who lost job
OL,4,Cafter strokes settles case for #100,000
OL,6,FIn the summer of 2023, the company
OL,7,Frecruited a new site manager who was
OL,8,Fyounger. Mr Donaldson was told that
OL,9,Fhis own employment would end in
OL,10,FSeptember 2023.
OL,12,FHe alleged that he was told the new
OL,13,Fsite manager would now manage the
OL,14,Fhousing construction over three sites.
OL,16,FMr Donaldson said he was later offered
OL,17,Fa potential consultancy role to
OL,18,Fcommence after his employment ended,
OL,19,Fbut he says it came with no guarantee
OL,20,Fof hours or duration.
