OL,6,FHe did not take up this offer and his
OL,7,Femployment with the company finished
OL,8,Fin September 2023.
OL,10,FMr Donaldson said: "This has been a
OL,11,Fvery difficult experience for me and
OL,12,Fmy family.
OL,14,F"I was shocked to learn I was being
OL,15,Freplaced, and that my employment was
OL,16,Fending.
OL,18,F"I wanted to continue working. It was
OL,19,Fan awful way to be treated after years
OL,20,Fof dedication to the business.
