OL,3,C'I felt abandoned': Man who lost job
OL,4,Cafter strokes settles case for #100,000
OL,6,F"I believe assumptions were made about
OL,7,Fmy ability following my strokes. I
OL,8,Fneeded some understanding.
OL,10,F"Instead, I felt abandoned, like I was
OL,11,Fonly fit for the scrap heap because of
OL,12,Fmy strokes and my age.
OL,14,F"I'm relieved the case is settled and
OL,15,FI can move forward."
