OL,6,FGeraldine McGahey, chief commissioner
OL,7,Fof the Equality Commission, said:
OL,8,F"Employers must be aware that
OL,9,Femployees like Cliff who acquire a
OL,10,Fdisability have protections under the
OL,11,FDisability Discrimination Act.
OL,13,F"They simply cannot make assumptions
OL,14,Fabout their employees' workplace
OL,15,Fcapabilities.
OL,17,F"Instead, they must communicate
OL,18,Fclearly with employees to fully
OL,19,Funderstand their needs.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
