OL,6,F"The law requires that reasonable
OL,7,Fadjustments must be considered and
OL,8,Fimplemented where appropriate. It is
OL,9,Fvital that all staff, especially line
OL,10,Fmanagers, are fully informed of these
OL,11,Fobligations."
OL,13,FShe added: "The Equality Commission
OL,14,Fprovides expert advice and practical
OL,15,Fguidance to help employers develop
OL,16,Feffective policies and procedures.
OL,18,F"Making use of this support will help
OL,19,Fensure compliance with Northern
OL,20,FIreland's equality laws and create a
OL,21,Fmore inclusive workplace".
