OL,6,FIn settling the case, Fraser Partners
OL,7,FLtd affirmed its strong commitment to
OL,8,Fthe principle of equality of
OL,9,Fopportunity in employment.
OL,11,FThe company also undertook to liaise
OL,12,Fwith the Equality Commission for
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland to review its
OL,14,Fpolicies and procedures.
